# A+ Phase 1.2: local pre-commit gate.
#
# Runs lint-staged so only the files you're about to commit are
# checked (fast), rather than the full repo. Keeps commit latency
# low while still catching local errors before they reach CI.
#
# Lint errors block the commit. Warnings pass through — fix them at
# your own pace. Bypass with --no-verify ONLY in emergencies; every
# bypass becomes tech debt.
npx lint-staged
